WEBVTT

01:36.070 --> 01:41.200
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.330 --> 01:43.990
[Episode 9]

01:44.340 --> 01:47.740
[Xigu Lane]

01:45.310 --> 01:47.479
Dry weather!

01:48.090 --> 01:50.789
Beware of fire!

01:56.950 --> 01:58.950
I have experience in these matters.

02:00.070 --> 02:01.880
There's no need to rush it.

02:02.350 --> 02:04.480
Silly girl, what do you know?

02:05.480 --> 02:07.120
Men's prime is shorter than women's,

02:07.120 --> 02:07.840
you know?

02:08.360 --> 02:11.280
When young, they have the desire
but not the guts

02:11.400 --> 02:12.660
because they're poor.

02:12.840 --> 02:13.800
In their prime,

02:13.800 --> 02:15.190
they have the guts but not the desire

02:15.190 --> 02:16.450
because they're busy.

02:17.030 --> 02:19.280
By the time they have
both the desire and the guts,

02:19.280 --> 02:20.610
the abilities are gone.

02:21.680 --> 02:23.510
So you must act early

02:23.530 --> 02:25.130
in order to have good babies.

02:27.030 --> 02:28.190
Mrs. Zhao.

02:29.390 --> 02:30.430
Fine.

02:31.079 --> 02:32.740
Let me give you another trick.

02:34.120 --> 02:36.430
During the day, I washed the bedding

02:37.030 --> 02:38.680
you use on the floor.

02:40.250 --> 02:42.850
He won't let you
sleep on the bare floor, right?

03:31.120 --> 03:31.840
Come here.

03:34.079 --> 03:34.590
Me?

03:35.630 --> 03:37.030
Why would I go there?

03:39.430 --> 03:40.760
There's only one quilt.

03:41.470 --> 03:42.800
If you don't sleep here,

03:43.150 --> 03:44.750
you're going to catch a cold.

03:45.840 --> 03:47.300
I'm not afraid of the cold.

03:58.560 --> 03:59.160
Come here.

04:12.470 --> 04:14.070
If you don't come sleep here,

04:14.810 --> 04:16.940
Mrs. Zhao won't sleep a wink all night.

04:24.950 --> 04:26.830
Just as I predicted.

04:27.580 --> 04:29.310
She has to sleep in the bed.

04:29.770 --> 04:31.630
You always come up with bad ideas.

04:31.630 --> 04:32.600
If she really freezes,

04:32.600 --> 04:34.560
I'll have to take care of
another sick person.

04:34.560 --> 04:36.420
You're spitting all over my face.

04:44.680 --> 04:45.830
Don't worry.

04:46.560 --> 04:49.490
I don't have any
inappropriate thoughts toward you.

04:56.680 --> 04:59.080
Don't blame Mrs. Zhao for meddling either.

04:59.850 --> 05:01.190
She means well.

05:04.680 --> 05:05.560
I know.

05:33.970 --> 05:35.030
What are you doing?

05:35.470 --> 05:37.260
We have to put on a full act.

05:38.540 --> 05:39.390
We

05:39.950 --> 05:43.010
shouldn't let Mr. and Mrs. Zhao
wait outside all night.

05:50.800 --> 05:51.920
It worked.

05:53.540 --> 05:56.950
You said young people
have the desire but not the guts

05:57.420 --> 05:58.720
and older people

05:58.720 --> 06:00.680
have the guts but not the desire.

06:00.810 --> 06:02.060
If you ask me,

06:02.320 --> 06:06.400
there are plenty of young people
with both the desire and the guts.

06:07.720 --> 06:09.310
I just made a passing remark,

06:09.310 --> 06:11.360
and you're rambling on and on.

06:13.070 --> 06:13.560
Wait.

06:14.600 --> 06:15.950
You damn old man.

06:16.830 --> 06:18.430
You heard that by eavesdropping outside.

06:18.430 --> 06:18.950
I...

06:20.070 --> 06:21.920
You're the pot calling the kettle black.

06:21.920 --> 06:23.160
Aren't you eavesdropping too?

06:23.160 --> 06:24.430
I just enjoy this sort of thing.

06:24.430 --> 06:25.690
None of your business!

06:35.480 --> 06:37.110
I only learned of your background

06:37.110 --> 06:38.740
after Mr. Sun came.

06:40.480 --> 06:42.610
You're going to leave sooner or later,

06:42.680 --> 06:43.340
aren't you?

06:49.520 --> 06:50.780
I won't cling to you.

06:52.680 --> 06:54.750
You can leave whenever you want.

06:57.270 --> 06:58.480
For now...

06:59.720 --> 07:00.680
I can't go yet.

07:06.560 --> 07:07.390
That works.

07:13.720 --> 07:14.980
I have something to do.

07:17.090 --> 07:18.340
I have to stay here

07:19.290 --> 07:20.090
to do it.

07:26.830 --> 07:27.990
Let me be on top.

07:28.060 --> 07:29.220
You get some rest.

07:36.630 --> 07:37.360
That works.

08:07.180 --> 08:09.830
There's still a big bowl
of braised meat rice in the kitchen.

08:09.830 --> 08:12.090
If you're hungry, I'll heat it up for you.

08:13.430 --> 08:14.360
I'm not hungry.

08:20.110 --> 08:22.310
I wonder if Changning is sleeping well.

08:22.630 --> 08:24.960
She loves kicking off the covers at night.

08:25.150 --> 08:26.680
I haven't fed the falcon yet either.

08:26.680 --> 08:28.190
If you want to talk,

08:30.870 --> 08:32.470
can I ask you a few questions?

08:34.480 --> 08:35.240
Go ahead.

08:37.620 --> 08:40.580
What kind of people were your parents?

08:42.080 --> 08:42.809
Good people.

08:44.030 --> 08:45.290
How did they treat you?

08:46.930 --> 08:48.560
Just as well as ordinary parents

08:48.560 --> 08:50.200
treat their own children.

08:52.080 --> 08:53.440
If one day,

08:54.830 --> 08:56.160
they wanted to harm you,

08:57.800 --> 08:58.820
what would you do?

09:05.790 --> 09:08.910
When I was little,
my mother used to beat me.

09:09.460 --> 09:11.520
She'd hit my left hand, then my right.

09:12.120 --> 09:12.870
She was heavy-handed.

09:12.870 --> 09:14.160
It really hurt.

09:14.320 --> 09:15.880
But every time she finished,

09:15.880 --> 09:18.280
she'd still buy candy
for Changning and me.

09:20.830 --> 09:21.960
I'm not asking about

09:22.760 --> 09:24.550
such trivial grievances.

09:26.980 --> 09:27.870
I understand.

09:29.940 --> 09:31.430
What I mean is...

09:33.500 --> 09:34.900
People close to you

09:35.840 --> 09:37.750
won't ruthlessly hurt you.

09:39.110 --> 09:42.950
Even if there are arguments or conflicts,

09:43.290 --> 09:44.180
afterwards,

09:45.030 --> 09:47.690
they'll still buy candy
to quietly comfort you.

09:51.230 --> 09:52.900
But if someone

09:53.550 --> 09:55.150
genuinely wants to harm you,

09:56.480 --> 09:57.940
fundamentally speaking,

09:58.550 --> 10:00.750
that person isn't close to you anymore.

10:34.820 --> 10:36.680
Did you eat tangerine peel candy?

10:37.410 --> 10:39.650
You smell like tangerine peel candy.

10:39.680 --> 10:41.080
Did you have a nightmare?

10:44.280 --> 10:46.590
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

10:45.010 --> 10:46.400
Eating candy

10:47.480 --> 10:48.890
helps me sleep.

10:47.550 --> 10:48.830
♪ With very pale colors ♪

10:49.700 --> 10:52.540
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

10:51.390 --> 10:53.440
If you want more when you return,

10:52.970 --> 10:55.470
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

10:53.460 --> 10:54.470
I'll buy you some.

10:56.210 --> 10:57.860
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

10:58.370 --> 11:02.620
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

10:58.960 --> 11:00.050
Do you...

11:02.510 --> 11:03.360
want some now?

11:06.110 --> 11:08.680
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

11:09.280 --> 11:10.960
♪ The light shines ♪

11:11.700 --> 11:14.400
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

11:14.810 --> 11:17.530
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

11:18.010 --> 11:19.920
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

11:20.360 --> 11:25.220
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

11:27.540 --> 11:28.850
♪ I pray that our love ♪

11:28.880 --> 11:31.500
♪ Will never end ♪

11:32.180 --> 11:33.190
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

11:33.220 --> 11:35.520
♪ For a lifetime ♪

11:36.150 --> 11:40.230
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

11:40.700 --> 11:44.370
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

11:45.020 --> 11:46.000
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

11:46.020 --> 11:48.680
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

13:29.320 --> 13:32.180
What exactly are you looking for
in the Fan's house?

13:53.680 --> 13:54.630
Mr. Li?

14:01.530 --> 14:02.290
Run!

14:03.450 --> 14:04.050
No need.

14:06.360 --> 14:07.030
Seize them!

14:15.990 --> 14:17.450
I'll ask you one more time.

14:17.690 --> 14:19.750
What exactly does the Fan family have

14:20.080 --> 14:23.540
that's worth the Wei family's
Iron Suicide Warriors coming here for?

14:23.540 --> 14:25.080
Who exactly are you?

14:25.330 --> 14:26.590
How do you know who I am?

14:32.910 --> 14:33.910
Marquis of Wu'an?

14:34.380 --> 14:35.440
Why are you here?

14:37.800 --> 14:39.540
I've pried open the mouths

14:40.620 --> 14:42.640
of countless spies in the army.

14:43.870 --> 14:45.630
If you want to try,

14:47.040 --> 14:48.640
I can oblige you.

14:49.660 --> 14:51.120
It was the Prime Minister.

14:51.150 --> 14:52.610
He sent me to find a letter.

14:52.610 --> 14:53.600
What letter?

14:59.840 --> 15:00.440
Speak.

15:02.640 --> 15:04.840
You know the Prime Minister's methods.

15:05.390 --> 15:08.100
Why make things difficult
for a nobody like me?

15:08.850 --> 15:10.910
What else did the Prime Minister say?

15:21.840 --> 15:22.790
Mrs. Fan, are you hurt?

15:22.790 --> 15:23.630
Mr. Li.

15:24.970 --> 15:25.640
I'm sorry.

15:27.440 --> 15:29.720
May I ask your name, My Lord?

15:30.080 --> 15:32.210
I will set up a memorial tablet for you.

15:33.630 --> 15:35.760
It's my duty. There's no need for that.

15:40.030 --> 15:42.330
My lord is
the Martial Commandant of Jizhou,

15:42.330 --> 15:43.840
Li Huaian.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.160
Thank you, Lord Li.

15:50.360 --> 15:51.280
I am humbled.

15:51.720 --> 15:52.790
The rebels are rampant.

15:52.790 --> 15:53.630
After Mr. Mu He of Jizhou

15:53.630 --> 15:55.480
went to guard Lucheng personally,

15:55.480 --> 15:59.010
I was ordered to come here
to assist in suppressing the bandits.

15:59.520 --> 16:01.180
But why were these men in black

16:01.460 --> 16:02.620
hunting you down?

16:02.960 --> 16:04.090
I don't know either.

16:07.510 --> 16:09.280
Oh no. Yan Zheng!

16:12.070 --> 16:12.730
Follow her.

16:22.070 --> 16:23.330
Changyu is back.

16:27.030 --> 16:27.840
Changyu!

16:28.670 --> 16:30.200
Are you and Yan Zheng hurt?

16:30.200 --> 16:31.870
What's with the dead bodies at the door?

16:31.870 --> 16:32.470
I'm fine.

16:32.550 --> 16:33.960
Mrs. Zhao, please look after Changning.

16:33.960 --> 16:34.150
Okay.

16:34.150 --> 16:35.510
Don't let her get scared.

16:35.510 --> 16:36.510
Go inside, quick.

16:36.630 --> 16:37.320
Quickly.

16:37.960 --> 16:38.820
Don't come out.

16:39.000 --> 16:39.860
My Lord, you...

16:43.030 --> 16:45.550
You're that gentleman from last time?

16:45.670 --> 16:47.960
I was sent by the Jizhou Prefecture
to investigate the case.

16:47.960 --> 16:50.510
My Lord, you must investigate thoroughly.

16:50.510 --> 16:52.360
The Fan family is so unlucky.

16:52.360 --> 16:53.150
Yes.

16:58.440 --> 16:59.150
Yan Zheng!

17:02.550 --> 17:03.240
Move!

17:03.510 --> 17:04.240
Yan Zheng.

17:04.440 --> 17:05.240
Yan Zheng.

17:05.310 --> 17:06.440
Yan Zheng, wake up!

17:07.000 --> 17:07.680
Get up.

17:08.200 --> 17:08.829
Get up.

17:11.829 --> 17:13.089
-Yan Zheng!
-Changyu!

17:13.109 --> 17:13.829
Changyu!

17:15.290 --> 17:16.030
Mr. Zhao,

17:16.200 --> 17:17.400
come and check on him.

17:17.680 --> 17:18.540
Don't move him.

17:18.750 --> 17:20.950
Don't make the injuries worse.

17:21.640 --> 17:23.480
Let me take a look.

17:27.790 --> 17:28.920
Yan Zheng, wake up.

17:29.680 --> 17:30.480
Yan Zheng.

17:49.510 --> 17:50.440
Did your husband

17:50.460 --> 17:51.840
kill this one

17:52.110 --> 17:53.910
and the men in black downstairs?

17:56.680 --> 17:58.740
My husband used to be an armed escort.

17:58.840 --> 18:00.840
He's quite skilled in martial arts.

18:01.340 --> 18:02.310
Officer,

18:02.480 --> 18:04.610
you must uphold justice for us.

18:04.880 --> 18:06.850
This girl has a hard life.

18:06.960 --> 18:08.910
Her parents just passed away last month.

18:08.910 --> 18:11.590
She finally found a husband
to marry into the family.

18:11.590 --> 18:12.760
But now,

18:12.830 --> 18:15.130
he's been injured by these thugs too.

18:15.310 --> 18:18.070
If we can't find out
where these criminals came from,

18:18.070 --> 18:20.640
how will she survive in the future?

18:20.660 --> 18:22.510
My Lord!

18:22.920 --> 18:25.180
My Lord, there's a survivor downstairs.

18:25.890 --> 18:26.600
Don't worry.

18:26.600 --> 18:27.110
Okay.

18:30.430 --> 18:32.420
Mr. Zhao, take another look.

18:32.790 --> 18:33.880
Let me check again.

18:33.920 --> 18:35.670
Let me check again.

18:36.510 --> 18:39.300
My Lord, this matrilocal husband
is very suspicious.

18:39.300 --> 18:40.790
Shouldn't we take him back
for questioning?

18:40.790 --> 18:42.540
No rush. I know what I'm doing.

18:42.640 --> 18:44.200
Let's go check on that survivor first.

18:44.200 --> 18:44.510
Yes,

18:44.510 --> 18:45.070
My Lord.

18:48.720 --> 18:49.590
If I had known,

18:50.510 --> 18:52.710
I would have written the divorce papers

18:53.370 --> 18:55.370
and let you recover somewhere else.

18:56.480 --> 18:58.880
Then you wouldn't have to
suffer like this.

19:03.880 --> 19:08.750
I was ordered to kill
the Fan family's daughter

19:08.750 --> 19:10.770
and retrieve the letter.

19:11.070 --> 19:12.210
The letter?

19:21.310 --> 19:22.420
Fan Changyu!

20:17.880 --> 20:20.480
He's covered in blood

20:20.720 --> 20:23.230
and looks like he's badly hurt,

20:24.030 --> 20:27.110
but his pulse isn't weak at all.

20:28.000 --> 20:29.640
But he's lost so much blood.

20:33.440 --> 20:34.600
Strange.

20:35.240 --> 20:37.160
There are no new wounds.

20:37.750 --> 20:38.680
This blood

20:39.240 --> 20:41.550
is from old wounds reopening.

20:42.640 --> 20:44.500
Let me check the wound on his back.

20:45.750 --> 20:46.550
You're awake.

20:47.610 --> 20:49.060
Yan Zheng, you're awake?

20:52.460 --> 21:02.510
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

20:56.440 --> 20:57.660
I'm fine.

20:58.390 --> 21:00.000
It's all blood from other people.

21:00.000 --> 21:01.270
Help him onto the bed.

21:02.720 --> 21:03.590
Careful, careful.

21:03.370 --> 21:12.900
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

21:04.160 --> 21:05.590
Slowly, slowly.

21:12.070 --> 21:13.330
As long as you're okay.

21:13.970 --> 21:18.500
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

21:14.420 --> 21:15.680
As long as you're okay.

21:18.520 --> 21:23.510
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

21:24.060 --> 21:26.180
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

21:26.770 --> 21:29.570
♪ I find her there ♪

21:29.240 --> 21:30.200
Yan Zheng!

21:30.250 --> 21:34.690
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

21:34.040 --> 21:36.480
Don't worry. I'm okay.

21:35.550 --> 21:40.080
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

21:40.100 --> 21:45.090
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

21:43.070 --> 21:46.000
Changyu, the soldiers need a statement.

21:45.850 --> 21:47.860
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

21:48.350 --> 21:52.730
♪ I find her there ♪

21:49.220 --> 21:49.930
Go ahead.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.440
Take care of yourself.

21:54.440 --> 22:04.360
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

22:04.450 --> 22:05.260
[Travel Permit]

22:05.260 --> 22:06.360
[Yan of Yan Village,
Changle County, Xuzhou]

22:06.380 --> 22:07.380
[This is a formal report]

22:07.410 --> 22:08.710
[While escorting a convoy to Chongzhou,
he encountered bandits]

22:08.730 --> 22:10.140
[and was stranded in
Lin'an Town, Qingping County, Suzhou]

22:14.960 --> 22:15.880
Changyu.

22:17.070 --> 22:19.310
What does the Martial Commandant do?

22:21.300 --> 22:23.180
Mrs. Zhao, my surname is Li.

22:24.110 --> 22:24.960
Lord Li.

22:25.160 --> 22:26.070
Lord Li.

22:27.350 --> 22:28.830
Before, I thought

22:28.830 --> 22:30.640
you were just a frail scholar.

22:30.960 --> 22:33.890
I didn't expect you to be
a high official from Jizhou.

22:34.000 --> 22:35.440
Since I've come this time,

22:35.440 --> 22:37.510
I will definitely
identify all the criminals

22:37.510 --> 22:39.310
and bring justice to the people.

22:45.730 --> 22:46.350
The survivor

22:46.350 --> 22:48.550
has been taken back for interrogation.

22:49.680 --> 22:51.140
Just wait at home for news.

22:51.270 --> 22:52.510
Once the case is resolved,

22:52.510 --> 22:54.370
the authorities will inform you.

22:54.640 --> 22:55.400
Lord Li,

22:55.680 --> 22:57.030
if those people come back for revenge,

22:57.030 --> 22:58.070
what should we do?

22:58.270 --> 23:00.800
I know I shouldn't
ask too much about the case,

23:00.880 --> 23:02.480
but my sister is still young.

23:03.640 --> 23:04.920
I was thinking

23:04.940 --> 23:07.340
we could leave after the New Year
to lie low.

23:08.330 --> 23:09.730
You want to leave Lin'an?

23:14.720 --> 23:16.320
Is this your husband's idea?

23:16.830 --> 23:17.640
It's my idea.

23:17.790 --> 23:19.450
I'm the head of the household.

23:20.830 --> 23:21.790
I want to leave

23:22.960 --> 23:26.220
because I fear something like tonight
might happen again.

23:27.030 --> 23:29.240
Your parents and uncle
were killed one after another.

23:29.240 --> 23:30.350
Although you are the victim,

23:30.350 --> 23:31.420
you are also a witness.

23:31.420 --> 23:32.990
Until the case is solved,

23:33.240 --> 23:34.640
you cannot leave Lin'an.

23:36.640 --> 23:37.550
But rest assured.

23:37.550 --> 23:39.400
I will station
enough soldiers in the village.

23:39.400 --> 23:41.130
Naturally, we will protect you

23:41.170 --> 23:43.430
and your family until the case is solved.

23:44.170 --> 23:46.150
Lord Li, you are truly a saint.

23:46.270 --> 23:48.270
We are relieved to hear you say that.

23:48.720 --> 23:51.420
Search every house! Quickly!

23:52.200 --> 23:53.440
Within this county,

23:53.750 --> 23:57.580
I will absolutely not allow anyone
to harm the innocent.

23:57.750 --> 24:00.510
I will definitely
give the people an answer today.

24:00.510 --> 24:01.830
Search carefully!

24:02.440 --> 24:04.350
Don't let a single criminal escape!

24:04.350 --> 24:05.030
-Yes!
-Yes!

24:10.880 --> 24:11.590
Lord Li.

24:14.200 --> 24:15.910
Greetings, Lord Li.

24:17.230 --> 24:19.980
I heard criminals were causing trouble
in Xigu Lane,

24:19.980 --> 24:22.000
so I personally led men to take them down.

24:22.000 --> 24:23.790
I didn't expect to meet you here, Lord Li.

24:23.790 --> 24:24.660
Please forgive me

24:24.660 --> 24:26.320
for not welcoming you sooner.

24:27.160 --> 24:27.790
My Lord!

24:28.830 --> 24:29.640
My Lord!

24:32.270 --> 24:32.960
My Lord.

24:34.030 --> 24:37.070
I found a memorial tablet for
the Marquis of Wu'an in this courtyard.

24:37.070 --> 24:38.270
Please look, My Lord.

24:39.150 --> 24:40.940
How dare they

24:40.960 --> 24:43.240
privately mourn the Marquis of Wu'an?

24:43.580 --> 24:44.450
Look, My Lord.

24:46.570 --> 24:48.420
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

24:48.880 --> 24:49.480
Who is it?

24:49.920 --> 24:51.240
Whose house is this?

24:52.960 --> 24:55.310
My Lord, this is my house.

24:56.070 --> 24:56.590
You?

24:57.310 --> 24:58.750
Fan Changyu?

24:59.110 --> 25:00.160
You again?

25:00.180 --> 25:01.450
My Lord,

25:01.790 --> 25:03.630
does the Legal Code of Great Yin state

25:03.630 --> 25:06.000
that paying respects to
the Marquis of Wu'an is forbidden?

25:06.000 --> 25:07.080
You plebeian,

25:07.110 --> 25:08.540
how dare you talk back?

25:08.650 --> 25:10.560
Men, tie her up and take her back.

25:10.680 --> 25:12.110
Take the memorial tablet too.

25:12.110 --> 25:14.500
You're caught red-handed this time.

25:14.590 --> 25:16.170
Why am I not aware

25:16.190 --> 25:17.680
that the Imperial Court forbids
paying respects to the Marquis of Wu'an?

25:17.680 --> 25:18.440
Well...

25:20.500 --> 25:22.770
My Lord, you are a top scholar.

25:22.790 --> 25:23.650
Surely you know

25:23.680 --> 25:27.680
that the Marquis of Wu'an's evil deeds
are despised by civil officials?

25:29.400 --> 25:31.790
I also heard
that about him massacring a city,

25:31.790 --> 25:33.270
Grand Tutor Li...

25:33.270 --> 25:34.880
The Marquis of Wu'an's
past merits and faults

25:34.880 --> 25:37.010
will be judged by future generations.

25:37.510 --> 25:38.970
He fought for the country.

25:39.340 --> 25:40.550
He died honorably.

25:46.830 --> 25:48.240
Well...

25:50.070 --> 25:52.130
Paying respects to him is not a crime.

25:57.590 --> 25:58.650
Thank you, My Lord.

26:02.790 --> 26:05.610
My Lord, you truly enlightened me.

26:06.200 --> 26:08.020
I was too narrow-minded.

26:08.800 --> 26:10.000
In that case,

26:10.030 --> 26:11.640
Lord Li, please return to town first

26:11.640 --> 26:13.350
so I can report on the case.

26:13.370 --> 26:14.430
After you, My Lord.

26:14.640 --> 26:15.310
Please.

26:17.200 --> 26:18.410
Please.

26:25.800 --> 26:28.950
[Northwest Inn]

26:29.830 --> 26:30.960
Watch out, My Lord.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.270
Mind the steps.

26:38.240 --> 26:39.310
General, please stay.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.440
No need to see me off.

26:40.590 --> 26:41.270
Take care, My Lord.

26:41.270 --> 26:43.200
Forgive me for not walking you out.

26:49.070 --> 26:51.210
Say, this Li Huaian

26:51.400 --> 26:53.660
was expressionless the whole time.

26:54.300 --> 26:55.170
Why is that?

26:55.990 --> 26:58.430
Grand Tutor Li's faction
and Prime Minister Wei's faction

26:58.430 --> 26:59.790
have always been at odds.

26:59.790 --> 27:01.770
Every official in the court knows it.

27:01.770 --> 27:03.350
But when it comes to Lord Li,

27:03.350 --> 27:05.610
why did he speak up for
the Marquis of Wu'an?

27:03.410 --> 27:06.380
[Northwest Inn]

27:05.720 --> 27:06.690
Exactly.

27:07.960 --> 27:08.820
Think about it.

27:09.350 --> 27:11.550
If they've always been enemies,

27:12.310 --> 27:14.030
then why would Grand Tutor Li

27:14.200 --> 27:16.080
let his eldest grandson

27:16.140 --> 27:18.540
study under He Jingyuan
of the Wei faction?

27:20.160 --> 27:21.070
Is that so?

27:21.940 --> 27:24.410
Could there be a past connection?

27:28.240 --> 27:31.500
Who can guess what these
powerful officials are thinking?

27:33.720 --> 27:34.790
I am

27:35.160 --> 27:36.840
stuck in this backwater town.

27:37.080 --> 27:38.790
Even if the court farts,

27:38.840 --> 27:41.440
the stink is gone
by the time it reaches Lin'an.

27:42.510 --> 27:43.480
I say,

27:43.680 --> 27:44.790
this mess is all your fault.

27:44.790 --> 27:46.050
You gave me bad advice.

27:46.110 --> 27:47.920
I tried to flatter him
and got on his bad side instead.

27:47.920 --> 27:48.910
Yes, yes.

27:49.400 --> 27:50.270
It's my fault.

27:50.350 --> 27:50.880
It's all my fault.

27:50.880 --> 27:51.810
Enough, enough.

27:52.160 --> 27:54.090
Let's go back and rethink our plan.

27:56.510 --> 27:59.240
Finally got rid of
that bootlicking magistrate.

28:00.070 --> 28:00.640
My Lord.

28:01.400 --> 28:02.350
We found that

28:02.440 --> 28:05.240
these assassins
all carried a black iron whistle.

28:09.350 --> 28:10.680
Black iron whistles...

28:10.920 --> 28:11.780
The capital...

28:12.610 --> 28:14.670
Committing suicide upon failure...

28:16.960 --> 28:17.920
It does resemble

28:17.920 --> 28:21.120
the style of the Wei faction's
rumored Suicide Warriors.

28:21.750 --> 28:23.010
Who would have thought

28:24.050 --> 28:27.310
that the Marquis of Wu'an we searched for
on the front lines

28:27.990 --> 28:30.190
became a matrilocal husband in Lin'an?

28:31.030 --> 28:31.670
Who?

28:32.320 --> 28:33.780
He is the Marquis of Wu'an?

28:33.800 --> 28:34.930
That's impossible.

28:35.370 --> 28:37.830
The Marquis of Wu'an
has such a fiery temper.

28:37.880 --> 28:39.460
Never mind that he's in trouble now,

28:39.460 --> 28:41.800
but even if His Majesty
threw him in the Imperial Prison

28:41.800 --> 28:44.170
to force him to marry the Eldest Princess
and join the imperial family,

28:44.170 --> 28:45.570
he still wouldn't agree.

28:45.600 --> 28:47.400
When we were young,

28:47.920 --> 28:51.520
we studied martial arts
and strategy together with our teacher.

28:51.590 --> 28:52.680
Though we haven't met in over a decade,

28:52.680 --> 28:54.480
and his appearance has changed,

28:55.090 --> 28:56.560
I am 60 percent sure

28:57.350 --> 28:58.210
that it was him.

28:59.880 --> 29:01.280
Whether it was him or not,

29:01.790 --> 29:03.450
deliver this quickly Yanzhou

29:03.730 --> 29:04.670
and we will know.

29:07.930 --> 29:10.250
[Xigu Lane]

29:13.880 --> 29:14.920
That's all.

29:15.510 --> 29:17.560
The harvest is bad this year.

29:17.590 --> 29:19.320
It's the same for every family.

29:26.040 --> 29:27.550
Have you heard?

29:27.680 --> 29:29.740
People died at the Fan's house again.

29:30.580 --> 29:31.890
After Fan Erniu and his wife

29:31.890 --> 29:33.830
died because of Changyu's bad luck,

29:33.830 --> 29:35.690
their family hasn't known peace.

29:36.750 --> 29:39.790
I heard her matrilocal husband
was badly hurt.

29:39.830 --> 29:42.640
Who knows if he can still
perform as a man.

29:44.350 --> 29:45.350
That Fan Changyu

29:45.400 --> 29:46.790
is a jinx.

29:46.980 --> 29:48.310
Scholar Song

29:48.310 --> 29:49.960
was lucky to break off the engagement.

29:49.960 --> 29:51.160
He escaped disaster.

29:51.270 --> 29:52.310
Scholar Song

29:52.310 --> 29:55.050
is the Star of Wisdom incarnate.
He's blessed.

29:55.210 --> 29:55.860
Yes.

29:57.220 --> 29:57.870
Yes.

30:03.240 --> 30:04.150
Who is that?

30:04.890 --> 30:05.660
I don't know.

30:10.270 --> 30:11.900
What do you want?

30:11.920 --> 30:13.340
We should be asking you.

30:13.720 --> 30:14.780
Where are you from?

30:14.880 --> 30:16.410
Why are you eavesdropping?

30:17.410 --> 30:19.070
We are from Jizhou Prefecture.

30:19.070 --> 30:20.190
We are old friends of the Fan family.

30:20.190 --> 30:21.590
Hearing news about them,

30:22.160 --> 30:24.090
we couldn't help but be concerned.

30:24.720 --> 30:27.930
Strangers prying
right after the Fan family incident?

30:28.060 --> 30:30.040
They must be up to no good.

30:30.160 --> 30:32.690
I say we report
to the officials immediately.

30:32.960 --> 30:36.020
Judging by his looks,
he doesn't seem like a bad person.

30:36.030 --> 30:38.430
Villains don't have labels on their faces.

30:38.640 --> 30:40.000
I certainly won't

30:40.240 --> 30:42.240
waste everyone's time for nothing.

30:49.960 --> 30:50.720
Let me tell you.

30:50.720 --> 30:51.640
I know.

30:52.810 --> 30:54.100
I'll talk.

30:55.110 --> 30:56.720
Martial Commandant!

30:58.270 --> 30:59.440
Hello.

30:59.690 --> 31:01.070
You're still in the village?

31:01.070 --> 31:02.000
You haven't left yet?

31:02.000 --> 31:02.530
Yes, yes.

31:03.400 --> 31:04.510
What's going on?

31:05.480 --> 31:07.380
What... Who is this?

31:07.790 --> 31:10.270
He's a big official from Jizhou
to investigate the case.

31:10.270 --> 31:11.240
A big official?

31:11.400 --> 31:13.140
I still have some questions.

31:15.680 --> 31:16.680
I don't know them well!

31:16.680 --> 31:17.400
Take it back.

31:17.400 --> 31:18.550
We haven't asked yet!

31:18.550 --> 31:18.960
Honestly.

31:18.960 --> 31:19.790
Mrs. Zhao.

31:20.070 --> 31:20.590
Sir,

31:21.210 --> 31:22.530
do you still want this?

31:26.310 --> 31:27.160
Zhao.

31:27.180 --> 31:28.120
Zhao.

31:28.350 --> 31:29.200
That...

31:29.790 --> 31:31.880
What does that Commandant guy do?

31:33.310 --> 31:34.350
I don't know.

31:34.440 --> 31:36.920
But even the magistrate is polite to them.

31:39.750 --> 31:40.480
Ladies.

31:41.330 --> 31:42.110
Don't ask us.

31:42.110 --> 31:42.720
We don't know.

31:42.720 --> 31:43.510
We're not close to the Fan family.

31:43.510 --> 31:44.110
Not close.

31:44.180 --> 31:45.240
Just one question!

32:06.480 --> 32:08.410
Sir, I'd like to ask...

32:08.440 --> 32:10.160
I don't know.

32:17.030 --> 32:18.880
My Lord, I didn't find out much.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.560
No one is willing to talk.

32:20.720 --> 32:23.070
I only know Mrs. Fan
wanted to keep her property,

32:23.070 --> 32:25.110
so she took in an outsider
named Yan Zheng as a husband.

32:25.110 --> 32:26.510
He was injured by bandits

32:26.510 --> 32:27.710
and saved by Mrs. Fan.

32:27.960 --> 32:30.160
Based on the travel permits we checked,

32:30.720 --> 32:32.380
there's nothing suspicious.

32:32.590 --> 32:34.850
If the Marquis of Wu'an planned all this,

32:35.160 --> 32:37.090
we certainly won't find anything.

32:37.640 --> 32:39.500
Why not ask the Zhao family again?

32:39.680 --> 32:41.240
Mrs. Zhao looks shrewd,

32:41.310 --> 32:43.370
but her husband seems easy to talk to.

32:44.070 --> 32:46.200
Given their relationship with Changyu,

32:46.200 --> 32:47.880
their testimony might be biased.

32:47.880 --> 32:48.480
True.

32:53.790 --> 32:54.590
My Lord.

33:00.110 --> 33:02.830
You want to know about the Fan family?

33:05.000 --> 33:06.810
I actually know quite a lot.

33:07.750 --> 33:09.000
It's just that...

33:16.550 --> 33:17.270
My Lord,

33:17.590 --> 33:18.680
that Fan Changyu

33:18.680 --> 33:20.330
is cursed.

33:20.350 --> 33:22.400
She didn't just curse
her parents to death.

33:22.400 --> 33:24.330
She even cursed her uncle to death.

33:25.070 --> 33:27.840
And that husband of hers

33:27.880 --> 33:29.200
is quite handsome,

33:29.620 --> 33:32.760
but he has no backbone at all.

33:33.270 --> 33:34.490
During the wedding ceremony,

33:34.490 --> 33:37.530
he actually swore
to obey Fan Changyu in everything.

33:37.640 --> 33:39.330
He just lives off her.

33:39.590 --> 33:43.320
You mean he publicly acknowledged Mrs. Fan
as the head of the house?

33:44.110 --> 33:46.000
All the villagers saw and heard it.

33:46.000 --> 33:48.070
I'm not making this up.

33:51.550 --> 33:52.160
My Lord,

33:52.510 --> 33:54.170
I'll tell you another secret.

33:55.360 --> 33:56.670
That Fan Changyu

33:56.730 --> 34:00.130
and her matrilocal husband
are likely just putting on a show.

34:00.480 --> 34:02.140
They haven't shared a bed yet.

34:02.680 --> 34:05.550
Fan Changyu is still a virgin.

34:07.070 --> 34:08.610
Watch your filthy tongue.

34:08.639 --> 34:10.239
Do not defile My Lord's ears.

34:10.630 --> 34:11.230
It's fine.

34:12.150 --> 34:12.960
Let her speak.

34:13.110 --> 34:15.370
What's there to be ashamed of?

34:15.510 --> 34:17.540
Her brows are still tight

34:17.840 --> 34:18.960
and her steps are light.

34:18.960 --> 34:20.590
If that doesn't make her a virgin,

34:20.590 --> 34:21.699
then what is she?

34:21.880 --> 34:22.610
Understood.

34:22.659 --> 34:23.820
We've heard enough.

34:24.040 --> 34:25.770
Thank you for the information.

34:27.150 --> 34:28.080
My Lord, My Lord!

34:30.510 --> 34:32.219
You must not tell anyone

34:32.250 --> 34:34.290
that I was the one who told you.

34:34.400 --> 34:35.540
You know,

34:35.560 --> 34:37.889
Fan Changyu used to be a butcher.

34:37.920 --> 34:39.380
She has immense strength.

34:39.380 --> 34:40.580
I've experienced it.

34:42.370 --> 34:42.960
My Lord.

34:42.960 --> 34:43.480
All right, enough.

34:43.480 --> 34:45.280
-I have more.
-Thank you, madam.

34:45.920 --> 34:46.630
Stop following us.

34:46.630 --> 34:48.280
I haven't finished yet!

34:50.510 --> 34:51.670
How could the dignified Marquis of Wu'an

34:51.670 --> 34:53.190
publicly acknowledge a woman as his master

34:53.190 --> 34:54.590
and become a matrilocal husband?

34:54.590 --> 34:56.760
My Lord, how certain are you now?

34:58.380 --> 34:59.380
Seventy percent.

35:01.840 --> 35:02.840
Seventy percent?

35:02.980 --> 35:04.360
How come it went up?

35:04.790 --> 35:08.110
[Changzhou Magistrate]

35:06.920 --> 35:09.440
The terrain east of Chongzhou
is precipitous.

35:09.440 --> 35:10.190
Easy to defend and hard to attack,

35:10.190 --> 35:11.650
it is a natural barrier.

35:11.420 --> 35:14.140
[Magistrate]

35:11.880 --> 35:13.510
If the enemy holds their ground here,

35:13.510 --> 35:14.630
our army will struggle to cross.

35:14.210 --> 35:18.940
[The world is benevolent]

35:15.360 --> 35:16.110
General,

35:16.110 --> 35:18.670
perhaps we can go through
Mount Heng's ravine

35:18.670 --> 35:20.050
to launch a flanking maneuver.

35:20.050 --> 35:23.590
[He Jingyuan, Prefect of Jizhou]

35:20.190 --> 35:21.920
We can bypass their front defense line

35:21.920 --> 35:24.180
and attack their flank or rear directly.

35:33.190 --> 35:35.190
Why is the magistrate's open office

35:35.310 --> 35:37.170
closed so tightly during the day?

35:37.710 --> 35:38.800
Or does

35:37.970 --> 35:41.740
[Wei Xuan, son of Wei Yan]

35:39.280 --> 35:41.710
General He have some unspeakable secret?

35:45.800 --> 35:48.400
Why did that rascal Li Huaian
go to Lin'an Town?

35:49.440 --> 35:50.840
Is Old Man Li

35:51.530 --> 35:53.260
targeting my Wei family again?

35:55.070 --> 35:57.670
Bandits are rampant around Lin'an.

35:58.280 --> 35:59.810
I sent him to suppress them.

36:00.070 --> 36:02.670
He encountered a murder case in town,

36:02.840 --> 36:04.510
so he was delayed for a few days.

36:04.510 --> 36:06.800
He will return
once he finishes investigating.

36:06.800 --> 36:07.920
General He,

36:09.320 --> 36:11.490
stop protecting your good student.

36:11.510 --> 36:13.640
A sixth-rank commandant

36:14.070 --> 36:17.000
going to a remote backwater town
to capture bandits?

36:18.190 --> 36:19.510
He clearly wants to use this chance

36:19.510 --> 36:21.240
to smear the Wei family's name.

36:22.230 --> 36:24.430
Watch your words, Eldest Young Master.

36:24.760 --> 36:25.670
Eldest Young Master,

36:25.670 --> 36:28.510
you already control
the military in Yanzhou.

36:29.190 --> 36:30.880
Why did you suddenly change course

36:30.880 --> 36:33.280
and come here to Jizhou?

36:36.070 --> 36:38.070
Xie Zheng has always been arrogant.

36:38.670 --> 36:41.630
Naturally, his soldiers
don't listen to orders.

36:43.320 --> 36:44.670
If I go to take over...

36:46.530 --> 36:48.590
I'm afraid something might go wrong.

36:51.180 --> 36:51.970
General He.

36:53.550 --> 36:56.520
Subdue Xie Zheng's Yanzhou troops for me.

36:56.720 --> 36:58.000
Then we'll press on

36:58.000 --> 36:59.930
and take Prince Changxin's Chongzhou City.

36:59.930 --> 37:01.010
Once we succeed,

37:01.920 --> 37:04.650
we'll be the greatest heroes
in my father's eyes.

37:09.840 --> 37:11.040
Eldest Young Master,

37:11.320 --> 37:14.960
Prince Changxin suffered setbacks
against the Marquis of Wu'an.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.690
He lost several major battles,

37:16.850 --> 37:18.450
and retreated to Chongzhou,

37:19.030 --> 37:21.270
but his main force is intact,

37:21.360 --> 37:23.290
and he still has capable generals.

37:23.400 --> 37:25.760
Eldest Young Master,
you've traveled a long way.

37:25.760 --> 37:27.960
We shouldn't rush into battle.

37:28.030 --> 37:29.160
Quite the opposite.

37:29.760 --> 37:32.230
Prince Changxin
has lost consecutive battles,

37:32.230 --> 37:33.440
and the Chongzhou army's morale is low.

37:33.440 --> 37:35.370
This is the perfect time to strike!

37:39.280 --> 37:40.110
General He,

37:40.670 --> 37:43.470
I respect you as a veteran general
under my father,

37:43.590 --> 37:45.970
which is why I came here personally.

37:46.670 --> 37:47.840
This is an order,

37:48.400 --> 37:49.400
not a suggestion.

37:53.710 --> 37:55.910
I expect your cooperation, General He.

38:11.650 --> 38:14.070
[Chongde Hall]

38:12.000 --> 38:13.130
Prime Minister Wei!

38:16.070 --> 38:17.800
What is the matter, Grand Tutor?

38:17.800 --> 38:18.800
Prime Minister Wei,

38:18.800 --> 38:20.400
in the Battle of Jinzhou years ago,

38:20.400 --> 38:21.920
General Xie died in battle.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.030
More than a decade later,

38:23.030 --> 38:25.760
the fate of the Marquis of Wu'an
is still unknown.

38:26.000 --> 38:29.400
Yet you still sent your only heir

38:29.400 --> 38:30.840
to the Northwest.

38:31.840 --> 38:34.090
When it comes to loyalty to Great Yin,

38:34.590 --> 38:37.920
no one compares to you,
Prime Minister Wei.

38:38.400 --> 38:39.880
There is an ancient saying:

38:39.880 --> 38:41.480
"Though our country is vast,

38:41.480 --> 38:43.140
not an inch shall be yielded."

38:43.280 --> 38:47.140
The sons of the Wei and Xie families
can die on the battlefield for this

38:47.480 --> 38:49.030
with no regrets.

38:50.280 --> 38:54.140
Then we shall await the triumphant return
of Eldest Young Master Wei.

38:54.550 --> 38:58.480
I congratulate you in advance.

39:00.190 --> 39:02.230
Then I must also congratulate you,
Grand Tutor.

39:02.230 --> 39:05.670
Your grandson has been promoted
to Martial Commandant.

39:05.840 --> 39:08.400
Sending him to the Northwest
for training at such a young age

39:08.400 --> 39:10.400
was great foresight.

39:11.070 --> 39:12.280
When he returns,

39:13.030 --> 39:15.360
he will surely be a pillar of the state.

39:18.190 --> 39:21.590
For 16 years,
my original intention has not changed.

39:21.590 --> 39:23.320
I work solely for Great Yin.

39:23.800 --> 39:25.280
I am open and honorable.

39:25.720 --> 39:27.350
Open and honorable?

39:27.880 --> 39:29.680
The Grand Tutor from 16 years ago

39:30.000 --> 39:33.360
could not bear the weight of those words.

39:41.670 --> 39:42.280
Hey...

39:42.630 --> 39:44.360
The Northwest Army
belongs to the Great Yin Dynasty.

39:44.360 --> 39:47.110
Does he think the Northwest
is the Wei family's backyard?

39:47.110 --> 39:49.360
Wei Yan is too arrogant.

40:28.400 --> 40:30.230
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

40:30.400 --> 40:32.800
It is time to hand it over.

40:31.620 --> 40:33.490
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

40:34.230 --> 40:36.480
When you handed it to me back then,

40:36.480 --> 40:38.340
you knew this day would come.

40:39.710 --> 40:41.320
You wanted me

40:41.100 --> 40:45.330
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

40:41.760 --> 40:43.960
to take good care of your two daughters.

40:46.590 --> 40:47.700
Pei Yi.

40:48.670 --> 40:50.240
This is urgent.

40:50.590 --> 40:53.320
Deliver this to Prime Minister Wei
immediately.

40:53.710 --> 40:54.280
Yes, sir.

41:02.000 --> 41:02.880
Come out.

41:03.550 --> 41:05.550
At the council hall this afternoon,

41:05.760 --> 41:08.630
I knew you were hiding nearby.

41:13.770 --> 41:15.790
I was afraid I came at the wrong time.

41:16.280 --> 41:18.390
After all, my identity is sensitive.

41:18.710 --> 41:19.620
Wenkan,

41:20.510 --> 41:22.110
I sent you to suppress bandits.

41:22.110 --> 41:23.710
What is there to be afraid of?

41:24.880 --> 41:27.150
I am worried that my identity
as a member of the Li family

41:27.150 --> 41:28.880
will bring criticism upon you.

41:28.960 --> 41:30.550
In front of Prime Minister Wei,

41:30.550 --> 41:32.280
it would just add to the gossip.

41:34.760 --> 41:35.760
Wenkan,

41:36.760 --> 41:38.320
count carefully.

41:38.920 --> 41:40.920
How many years have you been with me?

41:41.110 --> 41:43.000
Since I came to the Northwest as a child

41:43.000 --> 41:45.330
and learning military strategy from you,

41:45.510 --> 41:47.710
it has been 16 years.

41:49.630 --> 41:51.160
Then you should know that

41:52.110 --> 41:53.670
in my eyes,

41:54.360 --> 41:57.510
there is no conflict
between the Li and Wei families.

41:57.840 --> 42:00.510
There is only the army of Great Yin

42:00.800 --> 42:02.360
and the people of Great Yin.

42:03.190 --> 42:06.330
If you have a clear conscience,

42:06.440 --> 42:10.110
there is no need to avoid suspicion
because of your surname.

42:13.740 --> 42:14.450
By the way,

42:15.150 --> 42:18.030
have you made any progress
on the matter I asked you to investigate?

42:18.030 --> 42:19.030
I discovered

42:19.150 --> 42:22.190
Prime Minister Wei's Suicide Warriors
raided the Fan family twice.

42:22.190 --> 42:24.000
They are obviously looking for something.

42:24.000 --> 42:25.000
Fortunately,

42:25.230 --> 42:26.890
Mrs. Fan was not harmed.

42:27.080 --> 42:28.110
However, they already have thoughts

42:28.110 --> 42:29.320
of leaving Lin'an.

42:30.030 --> 42:32.190
I stopped them under the pretext
of investigating the case.

42:32.190 --> 42:34.000
I have asked Zhuoran
to protect them in secret.

42:34.000 --> 42:35.150
It is safer this way.

42:35.610 --> 42:39.030
How are Mrs. Fan and her sister doing?

42:39.550 --> 42:41.400
They make a living butchering pigs.

42:41.400 --> 42:42.860
She just took a husband in.

42:44.710 --> 42:45.320
Master,

42:46.360 --> 42:48.920
I have a lead on another matter.

42:52.670 --> 42:54.000
If the Marquis of Wu'an

42:54.510 --> 42:55.730
truly were alive,

42:56.190 --> 42:56.880
what should we do?
